                  Set in a fictionalized medieval world under oppressive noble rule, Bellwright
                  casts the player as a fugitive falsely accused of regicide who must survive in
                  the wilderness, build a settlement, recruit followers, and ultimately lead a
                  rebellion to topple the regime that destroyed their life. The game blends
                  mechanics from several popular genres: <strong>open-world survival</strong>,{' '}
                  <strong>colony/settlement management</strong>, <strong>medieval combat</strong>,
                  and <strong>strategy-level resource logistics</strong> — a combination that
