                  can design the layout of their settlement, customizing the placement of
                  structures, storage, and defensive fortifications. As the settlement grows,
                  it attracts more potential followers and unlocks higher-tier crafting,
                  research, and training options.
                </p>

                <h3 id="combat" className="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Combat &amp; Rebellion</h3>
                <p className="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
